24
00:01:27,640 --> 00:01:28,319
Alright.

25
00:01:28,760 --> 00:01:29,560
Go.

26
00:01:40,120 --> 00:01:41,439
Good thing I was in line to save you.

27
00:01:41,439 --> 00:01:42,000
I made it in time.

28
00:02:02,680 --> 00:02:03,760
