43
00:02:34,680 --> 00:02:35,000
I...

44
00:02:35,000 --> 00:02:35,719
Yang Xiaoxin.

45
00:02:36,879 --> 00:02:37,759
Where's your work?

46
00:02:41,319 --> 00:02:42,560
I haven't finished yet.

47
00:02:43,479 --> 00:02:44,520
The time isn't up.

48
00:02:45,240 --> 00:02:47,319
Don't give me useless excuses.

49
00:02:48,560 --> 00:02:50,120
Without a completed piece,

50
00:02:50,360 --> 00:02:52,960
you have no qualification
to compete at all.

51
00:02:55,719 --> 00:02:56,759
In that case,

52
00:02:57,439 --> 00:02:58,439
I announce

53
00:02:59,439 --> 00:03:01,199
that for this Dongfang Group's
Homecoming Banquet,

54
00:03:01,199 --> 00:03:02,560
the gown's designer

55
00:03:02,919 --> 00:03:04,280
will be Dong.

56
00:03:04,280 --> 00:03:05,280
Wait!

57
00:03:13,280 --> 00:03:14,080
Ms. Xi.

58
00:03:15,280 --> 00:03:17,199
If you're unwell, go to the hospital.

59
00:03:17,439 --> 00:03:19,639
This competition is already decided.

60
00:03:19,960 --> 00:03:21,199
Already decided?

61
00:03:23,199 --> 00:03:25,039
Since it was
an unfair competition to begin with,

62
00:03:25,400 --> 00:03:26,840
then let it be unfair to the end.

63
00:03:28,080 --> 00:03:30,680
Now, as the President of Vita,
I announce

64
00:03:31,280 --> 00:03:32,919
that the gown's designer

65
00:03:33,439 --> 00:03:34,919
will be Yang Xiaoxin.

66
00:03:37,000 --> 00:03:39,599
