of Vita immediately.

69
00:03:50,400 --> 00:03:51,479
And what are you supposed to be?

70
00:03:51,719 --> 00:03:52,439
He's the sec...

71
00:03:52,439 --> 00:03:52,960
Who is this man?

72
00:03:52,960 --> 00:03:53,719
Isn't he that...

73
00:03:53,960 --> 00:03:55,120
Ms. Xi, from the Dongfang family?

74
00:03:56,680 --> 00:03:57,479
