for Ms. Dongfang.

103
00:05:51,040 --> 00:05:52,240
For Ms. Dongfang?

104
00:05:52,240 --> 00:05:52,759
Yes.

105
00:05:52,759 --> 00:05:53,480
How dare she...

106
00:05:53,480 --> 00:05:55,160
It was my little sister's decision.

107
00:05:55,399 --> 00:05:56,199
Do you object?

108
00:05:59,240 --> 00:06:01,839
Didn't I say our Xiaoxin had potential?

109
00:06:02,399 --> 00:06:03,839
No wonder she's a talent I discovered.

110
00:06:05,959 --> 00:06:06,639
No...

111
00:06:06,639 --> 00:06:08,000
There's no need to exaggerate.

112
00:06:08,279 --> 00:06:08,800
Right?

113
00:06:09,160 --> 00:06:09,560
No...

114
00:06:09,560 --> 00:06:11,560
This employee of mine is simply humble.

115
00:06:12,040 --> 00:06:12,680
No...

116
00:06:12,680 --> 00:06:13,120
It's not...

117
00:06:13,120 --> 00:06:13,879
I... It's not...

118
00:06:14,040 --> 00:06:14,839
It's alright.

119
00:06:15,439 --> 00:06:16,560
What belongs to you,

120
00:06:16,560 --> 00:06:18,000
