no design company will dare to take him.

128
00:06:56,120 --> 00:06:57,319
What happened today

129
00:06:58,560 --> 00:07:00,600
is exactly as I've said.

130
00:07:01,560 --> 00:07:03,519
I don't want to hear a second version.

131
00:07:05,240 --> 00:07:06,560
Especially you.

132
00:07:07,480 --> 00:07:08,560
If you dare speak out,

133
00:07:09,079 --> 00:07:10,920
even Qiao Xi won't be able
to protect you.

134
00:07:14,360 --> 00:07:15,160
Yan,

135
00:07:15,759 --> 00:07:17,360
you let that man off so easily?

136
00:07:17,800 --> 00:07:18,879
He is Ye Yunzhou.

137
00:07:19,360 --> 00:07:20,160
Ye Yunzhou?

138
00:07:21,000 --> 00:07:22,240
That's Ye Yunzhou.

139
00:07:23,480 --> 00:07:24,519
That rotten scumbag.

140
00:07:24,519 --> 00:07:26,390
