166
00:08:27,720 --> 00:08:29,439
and now she's even close to Mr. Zhan.

167
00:08:30,839 --> 00:08:31,959
I've been hurt too many times

168
00:08:31,959 --> 00:08:33,320
because of that woman.

169
00:08:33,840 --> 00:08:35,440
I don't want her to hurt you again.

170
00:08:37,840 --> 00:08:38,840
Yunzhou.

171
00:08:39,919 --> 00:08:41,320
